{"tid":1796563,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣無左生存既目的","createTime":"2019-12-24T16:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T17:34:42.000Z","uid":36859,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3856a23cdf304cf35ab05dff3a727530ff94bc86","tid":1796563,"uid":36859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:47:04.000Z","msg":"我26歲 曾經有夢想同理想<br />\n但慢慢兩樣都消失左<br />\n搵唔到野做 無專長<br />\n係我人生最低谷既時候有個女仔出現<br />\n帶我出黎比左個希望我<br />\n成為左我人生既目標<br />\n因為佢我有好大既壓力 為左追上佢<br />\n我願意為左佢去做自己唔想做既野<br />\n就係為左同佢成家立室<br />\n佢就係我既人生推動力<br />\n但係係佢同我講分手之際<br />\n我一直諗 無左佢我可以為左啲咩努力工作<br />\n最後我發現 <br />\n其實我連生存既動力都無<br />\n我最想既就係可以快啲死<br />\n係香港我無希望 小小既希望我都見唔到<br />\n真係好辛苦。。。。"},{"pid":"0b7f611525b73de6c846a0a08afd823b555ebf31","tid":1796563,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:49:41.000Z","msg":"因她的出現而生<br />\n因她的離去而亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼曾經擁有過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef399eaaa9d1fab1aaf24f52a00250a6139af47","tid":1796563,"uid":36859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b7f611525b73de6c846a0a08afd823b555ebf31","tid":1796563,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:49:41.000Z","msg":"因她的出現而生<br />\n因她的離去而亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼曾經擁有過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:51:01.000Z","msg":"佢最後同我講既一句係 <br />\n咁你當我地無識過啦"},{"pid":"5c0fe8060b9a4961290c57fe2d24245183686b16","tid":1796563,"uid":202735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:53:07.000Z","msg":"關關難過關關 人生緊係咁啦"},{"pid":"26566db73c6a9de60899b8f648eea6bd50870d57","tid":1796563,"uid":295863,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:55:14.000Z","msg":"光復香港 社代革命<br />\n你嘅人生唔係淨得兒女私情"},{"pid":"63278f091295aa83902ad0c3257bccac15a87a6c"